 * RummyRoyal - Hero Slider Component
 * 
 * 全宽首屏区域，大标题、统计数据、CTA按钮和装饰性扑克牌形状
 * 
 * @var \Weline\Framework\View\Template $this
 * @var array $colors 颜色配置
 * @var array $component_config 组件配置
 * 
 * @fields_start
 * 
 * group:content => 内容设置
 * content.badge => 顶部徽章:text:🏆 #1 Rated
 * content.title => 主标题:textarea:India's Most Trusted Rummy Platform
 * content.description => 描述:textarea:Join millions of players on India's premier rummy platform. Play skill-based card games, compete in tournaments, and win real cash prizes with instant withdrawals.
